The article is about Vice President Pence's remarks during Made in America Week at the White House. Pence praises President Trump for his commitment to American manufacturing and his efforts to promote and protect American businesses. He highlights Trump's actions in slashing federal red tape, fighting for fair trade, unleashing American-made energy, and boosting the confidence of American manufacturers and farmers. Pence concludes by introducing President Trump as the 45th President of the United States.